snippet.title: FreakyFeet
snippet.description:
Welcome to FreakyFeet!

This channel is about everything gamedev and focuses on teaching Unity and whatever is needed in order to create a game!

- Learn how to make games using Unity

- Indie dev logs when I have a project going on

- Watch me fail at digital painting with Krita


Something about me:
My name is Aidin Dadashzadeh. I live in a town called Gävle in Sweden with my girlfriend and our two small daughters. Needless to say, I like making games!
During the day I work as a web developer, but my hopes and dreams are to be able to dedicate all my work time to this channel and making games.

Glad to have you and once again welcome to my quest!   - Taking the step


----------------------------------

Join me on Twitter: https://twitter.com/aidin_d
